Communication: Ability to translate complex technical concepts into clear language for stakeholders at all levels.
Agile Experience: Comfort working in collaborative, iterative environments with high-level organizational and prioritisation skills. 

Desirable

Squiz Matrix Expertise: Proven experience designing and developing complex solutions within the Squiz Matrix DXP environment (customisation, asset management, and template creation).

Experience implementing WCAG Digital Accessibility Standards.
Familiarity with integration of third-party web services (APIs).
Experience working within a Digital Design System.
Proficiency with web analytics tools to inform system optimisation.

