About the job
About the Company
 
Our client is a leading organisation within the banking sector, focused on delivering innovative digital solutions that enhance customer experience and drive real business value. With a strong emphasis on modern engineering practices, they offer a collaborative environment where technology and continuous improvement are at the core of everything they do.

 
About the Role

 
We're looking for a Full Stack Developer to join a high-performing team. In this role, you'll take ownership of key product modules, designing and building cloud-based applications, APIs, and microservices. You'll work closely with cross-functional teams including engineers, testers, business analysts, and designers to deliver high-quality, scalable solutions.
 

You'll also play a key role in mentoring others, contributing to technical direction, and ensuring best practices across development, testing, and delivery.

 
About You
 
You're a seasoned Full Stack Developer with strong experience across both backend and frontend technologies. You're comfortable working in Agile environments and enjoy collaborating with others to solve complex problems.
 
Key experience includes:
  Strong skills in Java and JavaScript
Experience with modern frameworks (e.g. React, Angular, Spring Boot)
Building and consuming APIs (REST, OpenAPI/Swagger)
Familiarity with cloud platforms (ideally AWS)
Experience with tools such as Git, Gradle, or Webpack
Strong understanding of testing practices (unit, integration)
Experience with Docker/Kubernetes and DevOps practices is a plus
Previous experience in banking or financial services is highly regarded

Please apply with current resume in Microsoft Word format only (.doc or .docx). If you would like to have a confidential discussion, please contact Dylan Tasker on dylan.tasker@davidsonwp.com , quoting reference JN -042026-42919. Want to know more about Davidson? Visit us at www.davidsonwp.com

