About the job
About Us
Nerd On Call Services (NOCS) is a growing digital company focused on helping businesses build and strengthen their online presence, community, and brand. We develop complete digital ecosystems for our clients, including websites, applications, and content strategies that drive engagement and organic growth.

Role Overview
We are seeking multiple Website Developers to support the design, development, and optimization of websites for client and internal projects. This role involves building responsive, high-performing websites that align with brand identity and support business goals.
Projects may include:
Business websites
Landing pages
E-commerce platforms
Portfolio and brand websites
Custom web solutions

Key Responsibilities
Design, develop, and maintain responsive websites
Collaborate with internal teams to align websites with branding and strategy
Optimize websites for performance, speed, and user experience
Integrate third-party tools, APIs, and platforms
Ensure mobile responsiveness and cross-browser compatibility
Troubleshoot and resolve technical issues
Maintain clean, organized code and documentation

Qualifications
